             was indicted for <rs id="t18251208-35-off166" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18251208-35-off166" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18251208-35-off166" type="offenceSubcategory" value="mail"></interp>
               that he, at the time of committing the several felonies and offences in the first eight counts of this indictment, hereinafter mentioned, was a <rs id="t18251208-35-viclabel167" type="occupation">person employed by and under the Post-office of Great Britain</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18251208-35-victim246 t18251208-35-viclabel167"></join>
